Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:23.50,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}起舞 躍動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:25.22,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}摸摸 蹭蹭 ahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:26.99,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.76,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}毛茸茸 鬆拋拋 ahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:30.53,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}起舞 躍動
